subSubSection.paragraph:
Variation.
Body length 23.6–24.9 mm; width 10.7–11.4 mm. Most individuals with orange-red tomentum (
Fig. 25, 28
) and wine-red metallic reflections, while a small number with yellow tomentum and green metallic reflections (
Figs. 26–27
). A few males with setae in the abdominal groove (
Fig. 28
).
